high_descs: Turn left to reach the remotecontrol on the living room table.
Pick up the remote control from the table.
Turn right and head to the room on the left to reach the shelf on the right.
Put the remotecontrol in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Put the RemoteControl in the Shelf.

high_descs: Turn right, after passing the remotecontrol, turn left. Before the end of the remotecontrol, turn left.
Turn right, when you are close to the wall, turn left. Go straight ahead and turn left at the entrance. Enter the room. After passing the shelf, turn left. Raise the remote control.
Place the remote control on the shelf on the far side of the top drawer in the second column.
anns.task_desc: Find a RemoteControl, place it on a Shelf.

high_descs: exit the room using the remotecontrol.
Collect the remotecontrol from the diningtable.
Turn right then turn left and go straight to the shelf.
Put the remotecontrol in the shelf.
anns.task_desc: Collect the RemoteControl from the dining table and keep inside the Shelf.
